<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"><strong><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;">《冬日丝语》音乐会</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">演出时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2012</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">12</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">9</span>日           </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">演出地点：国家大剧院音乐厅     </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">指挥：何建国（国家一级指挥）</span></p>
